{"article_id":"qsP01QvKNFrffEAE","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"With the president ' s stunning admission Monday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he has been taking hydroxychloroquine , an anti-malaria drug","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"most medical experts say","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"should not be used","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"to treat or prevent coronavirus ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the questions tumbled out .","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"Was Trump lying","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"about taking the drug","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he ' s long been touting","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to combat COVID-19 ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"just to own the libs ?","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Was he really taking it ,","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"and if so ,","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"why would an actual doctor prescribe it ?","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Was he putting his life on the line","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"by taking a drug","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"the FDA cautioned against outside of hospitals ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"and that has been linked to deaths ?","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Columnists","depth":2},{"id":20,"text":"In-depth political coverage , sports analysis , entertainment reviews and cultural commentary .","depth":3},{"id":21,"text":"But the news","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that Trump may be on a dangerous regimen of hydroxychloroquine","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"( while refusing to , much more simply , wear a mask in public )","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"didn ' t seem to alarm his supporters .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"A comment from Speaker Nancy Pelosi , on the other hand , did .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" He ' s our president ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" she told CNN Monday night ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" and I would rather he not be taking something","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that has not been approved by the scientists , especially in his age group and in his ,","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"shall we say ,","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"weight group","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"morbidly obese . \"","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"Now , the obvious reaction to this ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"regardless of your politics ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"is to laugh audibly and for at least a couple minutes ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"as I did ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"at Pelosi ' s not-so-subtle dig .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Unless , of course , you ' re a suddenly oh-so-sensitive Team Trump snowflake ,","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"in which case you clutch your MAGA hat","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and cry into your chloroquine at the outrage of Pelosi ' s \" fat-shaming \" of the president . \"","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"The same people","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"that lead the body positivity movement","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"apparently feel comfortable commenting on people ' s weight publicly .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Always good to remember","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"the rules never apply to them , \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"tweeted one very hurt person .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"\" I ' m wondering","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"if @ secupp and others would find it knee slapping hilarious \"","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"- and I did ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"as I mentioned -","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"\" if President Donald Trump called someone morbidly obese","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"or would the words fat shaming be trending ?","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"I want to make certain","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"we are playing by the same rule book , \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"tweeted another concerned citizen and astute observer of the president ' s notable past behavior .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"The earnestness","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"with which these \" asking for a friend \" posts about \" the rules \" were written","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"leads me to believe","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"they are not , in fact , joking .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"So ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"as a fan of intellectual consistency myself , I ' ll respond","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"by saying ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"\" Rules ?","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"Where we ' re going ,","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"we don ' t need rules. \"","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"I ' ll go ahead","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and show my work .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"The president has referred to women over the course of his public career as \" dogs , \" \" pigs , \" \" fat , \" \" ugly , \" \" slobs , \" \" lowlifes \" and \" horseface \" ;","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"He has bragged about grabbing women by the genitals ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and has been accused by no fewer than 25 women of sexual misconduct ;","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"He has attacked women journalists","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"for doing their jobs ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"and mused on multiple occasions that women are more suited for housework ;","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"He has mocked a girl with Asperger ' s , a disabled journalist , a prisoner of war , a Gold Star family and even his own supporters ;","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"He has called the media \" losers , \" \" nasty \" and \" human scum , \" accused one news anchor of murder ,","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"suggested","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"another was menstruating","depth":16},{"id":79,"text":"and that another was bleeding from a bad facelift ;","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"He insisted","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"former President Barack Obama was from Kenya ,","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"maligned immigrants from \" shithole countries , \"","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"said","depth":17},{"id":84,"text":"a gathering of neo-Nazis included \" some very fine people , \"","depth":17},{"id":85,"text":"and trafficked heavily in online anti-Semitic tropes .","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"I have a hunch","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"Trump fans are not all that offended on behalf of their insulter-in-chief","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"but are just playing the part out of boredom and unfulfilled promise .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"For some , the Pelosi comments finally unshackled them from the chains of common decency","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"so that they could engage in the real fat-shaming","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"they ' ve long wanted to do :","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"\" This bich","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"[ sic ]","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"literally just called @ realDonaldTrump ' morbidly obese on NATIONAL TV ! ! !","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"Bahhhahaha this is awesome ! !","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Sorry liberals , fat shaming is no longer an offence ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"and any heat towards this oiled up crypt keeper is game on , \"","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"tweeted one emancipated reveler .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"\" Glad she said it .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Cause now we can point out","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"that Lizzo is morbidly obese , \"","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"exclaimed another former fat-shamers anonymous member .","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"\" Is Stacy Abrams morbidly obese too ? \"","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"asked a curious health fan .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"For these fine folks , Pelosi apparently gave them a new lease on life .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"For the others , the Trump fans","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"who would very much like to speak to your manager about the so-called rules ,","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"let ' s talk","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"when Trump inevitably tweets out his well-thought-out retort to Pelosi .","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Because","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"when it comes to being offended ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Trump fans have not a 